ox;width: 3em;border-bottom: 2px solid rgb(63, 63, 63);float: right;word-wrap: break-word !important;"></section><section data-width="90%" style="margin-top: 3px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;clear: both;width: 172.797px;border-bottom: 2px solid rgb(63, 63, 63);float: right;word-wrap: break-word !important;"></section></section></section></section></section><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"></p><section style="margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 10px;margin-left: 16px;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);min-height: 1em;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">近年来，全国各地选择复读的考生呈现愈发增多的趋势，“复读热潮”渐渐掀起：</span></section><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"></p><section style="margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 10px;margin-left: 16px;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);min-height: 1em;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">2018广东高考成绩放榜第二天，大批前来报名复读的考生和家长在凌晨时就在学校门口排起了长队，因为招生计划有限，当校门一开，学生和家长们便立刻上演了百米冲刺。</span></section><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"></p><section style="margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 10px;margin-left: 16px;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);min-height: 1em;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">2019年8月，安徽毛坦厂中学，有近12000名复读生前来学校报到，有学生还称：自己的班级里就有10个同学是复读生。<br style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span></section><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><mpcpc js_editor_cpcad="" class="" src="/cgi-bin/readtemplate?t=tmpl/cpc_tmpl#1575261936284" data-category_id_list="1|11|16|17|22|24|26|27|28|29|3|31|32|35|36|37|39|41|42|43|45|46|47|48|49|5|50|51|52|53|54|55|6|7|8" data-id="1575261936284" style="display: none;"></mpcpc></p><section style="margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 10px;margin-left: 16px;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);min-height: 1em;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">2019年广东高考放榜后的一个月，某教育机构新一年的复读课程已开课。据该教育机构的负责人介绍称：已有超过1000名同学到校进班学习，各校区学位余额也不多，出现了供不应求的趋势。</span></section><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"></p><section style="margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 10px;margin-left: 16px;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);min-height: 1em;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">众多考生选择复读相关的新闻远远不止这些，这样的状况每年高考落榜时都会如期上演。</span></section><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-align: center;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"></p><section class="" data-tools="135编辑器" data-id="94065" style="max-width: 100%;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 10px;margin-left: 16px;max-width: 100%;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="max-width: 100%;display: flex;justify-content: center;align-items: center;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="padding: 3px 7px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;display: inline-block;background: rgb(255, 227, 10);border-radius: 6px;font-weight: bold;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">02</span></section><section style="margin-top: 6px;margin-left: 5px;max-width: 100%;display: inline-block;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section class="" data-brushtype="text" style="max-width: 100%;font-weight: bold;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 1.75em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">复读生群体数量到底有多庞大？</span></section><section style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;width: 3em;border-bottom: 2px solid rgb(63, 63, 63);float: right;word-wrap: break-word !important;"></section><section data-width="90%" style="margin-top: 3px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;clear: both;width: 201.594px;border-bottom: 2px solid rgb(63, 63, 63);float: right;word-wrap: break-word !important;"></section></section></section></section></section><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-align: center;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"></p><section style="margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 10px;margin-left: 16px;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);min-height: 1em;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">官网虽未公布近几年的数据，但清华大学“中国大学生学习与发展追踪研究”曾研究发现：</span></section><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"></p><section style="margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 10px;margin-left: 16px;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);min-height: 1em;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">2011-2018年，全国本科大学里第一代大学生（即特指父母没有读过大学、通过自己的不懈努力进入大学的学生）一直保持在70%以上的占比。</span><span style="max-width: 100%;color: rgb(55, 74, 174);font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">同时，与非第一代大学生相比，更多的第一代大学生参加过多次高考（即复读），占比达到19.91%。</strong><strong style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"></strong></span><br style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"></section><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"></p><section style="margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 10px;margin-left: 16px;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);min-height: 1em;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">如果据此推算的话，全国本科高校大学生中预计有17.47%的学生曾复读过。</span><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">据教育部发布的官方数据，<span style="max-width: 100%;color: rgb(55, 74, 174);box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">2019年全国高考报名人数达1031万，如果17.47%的考生为复读生的话，那么人数将高达180.1万。</strong><strong style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"></strong></span></span></section><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"></p><section style="margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 10px;margin-left: 16px;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);min-height: 1em;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">除此之外，随着教育的普及，每年高考报名人数都呈逐年上涨的趋势，复读生的数量也会随着增加。</span></section><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"></p><section style="max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="padding-right: 3px;padding-bottom: 3px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="padding: 20px 15px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;border-color: rgb(55, 74, 174);border-style: solid;border-width: 1px;box-shadow: rgb(55, 74, 174) 3px 3px 0px 0px;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 10px;margin-left: 16px;max-width: 100%;color: rgb(55, 74, 174);font-size: 14px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img data-type="png" class="" data-ratio="0.8304195804195804" data-w="572" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/UtIAWicWKRfo8ibPEf29tVVeU3fw23BL4HV1W3csvWKukU2KmU1AEkGYTDB5saaY8MKyStG0PvTavYLA63FlibkVA/640?wx_fmt=png" style="box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; visibility: visible !important; width: 520px !important; height: auto !important;" _width="520px" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/UtIAWicWKRfo8ibPEf29tVVeU3fw23BL4HV1W3csvWKukU2KmU1AEkGYTDB5saaY8MKyStG0PvTavYLA63FlibkVA/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;tp=webp&amp;wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1&amp;wx_co=1" crossorigin="anonymous" data-fail="0"></section></section></section></section><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"></p></section><section style="margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 10px;margin-left: 16px;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);min-height: 1em;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">如今，会选择复读的考生都是哪种类型的考生呢？</span><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">结果有点令人出乎意料！</span></section><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"></p><section style="margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 10px;margin-left: 16px;max-width: 100%;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">复读已不是落榜生“专利“</span></section><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"></p><section style="margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 10px;margin-left: 16px;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);min-height: 1em;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">在我们印象里，选择复读的考生一般都是因为高考发挥不好，和平时成绩差异较大的学生，我们通常称为“落榜生”。</span><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">不过近几年高分考生选择复读的现象愈来愈多，这一群体的复读生数量呈扩大趋势：</span></section><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"></p><section style="margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 10px;margin-left: 16px;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);min-height: 1em;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">在安徽毛坦厂中学，选择复读2020高考的理科考生里有高考分数高达<span style="max-width: 100%;color: rgb(55, 74, 174);box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">622分</strong></span>的考生；</span></section><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"></p><section style="margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 10px;margin-left: 16px;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);min-height: 1em;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">在深圳，有复读学校的校长在接受采访时发现：</span><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">高分考生准备复读的人数猛增，理科最高分可达到<span style="max-width: 100%;color: rgb(55, 74, 174);box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">568分</strong></span>，文科最高<strong style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%;color: rgb(55, 74, 174);box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">超</span></strong><span style="max-width: 100%;color: rgb(55, 74, 174);box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">600分</strong></span>；</span></section><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"></p><section style="margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 10px;margin-left: 16px;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);min-height: 1em;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">2017年高考本科录取进入尾声时，据广东多所机构反映：</span><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">复读生虽然还是以没能考上本科或者是未能考上重本的学生为主，但分数达到一本还选择复读的学生比例正在逐年增加。</span></section><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"></p><section style="margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 10px;margin-left: 16px;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);min-height: 1em;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">高分考生选择复读现象越来越普遍，各学校为了提高学校重本升学率也不惜使用各种“福利”来吸引高分生入读：</span><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">有的学校提供免费食宿，有的学校按照考生高考分数给予一定的学费优惠或者免除学费，有的在此基础上还另补助奖学金。</span></section><section style="margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 10px;margin-left: 16px;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);min-height: 1em;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"></section><section class="" data-tools="135编辑器" data-id="94065" style="max-width: 100%;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 10px;margin-left: 16px;max-width: 100%;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="max-width: 100%;display: flex;justify-content: center;align-items: center;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="padding: 3px 7px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;display: inline-block;background: rgb(255, 227, 10);border-radius: 6px;font-weight: bold;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">03</span></section><section style="margin-top: 6px;margin-left: 5px;max-width: 100%;display: inline-block;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section class="" data-brushtype="text" style="max-width: 100%;font-weight: bold;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 1.75em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">为何现在越来越多考生会选择复读呢？</span></section><section style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;width: 3em;border-bottom: 2px solid rgb(63, 63, 63);float: right;word-wrap: break-word !important;"></section><section data-width="90%" style="margin-top: 3px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;clear: both;width: 244.797px;border-bottom: 2px solid rgb(63, 63, 63);float: right;word-wrap: break-word !important;"></section></section></section></section></section><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-align: center;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"></p><section style="max-width: 100%;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="padding: 10px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 10px;margin-left: 16px;max-width: 100%;width: 567px;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="max-width: 100%;display: inline-block;width: auto;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="padding-right: 15px;padding-left: 15px;max-width: 100%;border-color: rgb(51, 51, 51);border-style: solid;border-width: 1px;height: 35px;line-height: 32px;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);transform: rotate(0deg);box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section data-brushtype="text" style="max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 1.5px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">公办院校学费比民办的低</span></section></section><section style="margin-top: -41px;margin-right: -6px;margin-left: 8px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;border-color: rgb(51, 51, 51);border-style: solid;border-width: 1px;height: 35px;background-image: -webkit-linear-gradient(left, rgb(196, 209, 255), rgb(205, 245, 254));color: rgb(254, 254, 255);word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"></section></section></section></section></section></section><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"></p><section style="margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 10px;margin-left: 16px;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);min-height: 1em;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">部分考生选择复读，主要原因不在于考不上大学，在于考不上公办大学。</span><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">毕竟公办高校的学费是远远低于民办高校的，比如：</span><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">哈尔滨工业大学（深圳）学费为6230元/年，而吉林大学珠海学院最低学费也需要26000元/年。</span></section><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"></p><section style="margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 10px;margin-left: 16px;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);min-height: 1em;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">这对家境一般的考生来说这无疑是巨大的经济压力，所以宁可选择复读，在来年高考中考取一所公办院校。</span></section><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"></p><section style="max-width: 100%;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="padding: 10px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 10px;margin-left: 16px;max-width: 100%;width: 567px;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="max-width: 100%;display: inline-block;width: auto;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="padding-right: 15px;padding-left: 15px;max-width: 100%;border-color: rgb(51, 51, 51);border-style: solid;border-width: 1px;height: 35px;line-height: 32px;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);transform: rotate(0deg);box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section data-brushtype="text" style="max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 1.5px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">名校文凭更“值钱”</span></section></section><section style="margin-top: -41px;margin-right: -6px;margin-left: 8px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;border-color: rgb(51, 51, 51);border-style: solid;border-width: 1px;height: 35px;background-image: -webkit-linear-gradient(left, rgb(196, 209, 255), rgb(205, 245, 254));color: rgb(254, 254, 255);word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"></section></section></section></section></section></section><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"></p><section style="margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 10px;margin-left: 16px;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);min-height: 1em;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">首先，在高校录取率攀升、大学扩招的今天，考取一所普通本科高校已不再是一件特别稀奇的事了，但如果考上了重本院校，是很令人骄傲的，也就是<strong style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%;color: rgb(55, 74, 174);box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">“听起来好听”</span></strong>（注：</span><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">这里的“好听”并不含贬义之意）。</span></section><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"></p><section style="margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 10px;margin-left: 16px;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);min-height: 1em;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">其次，社会竞争激烈，学历文凭已成为大学毕业生们找工作的一块“敲门砖”，而学校的知名度则是衡量你这块“敲门砖”很大影响因素。</span></section><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"></p><section style="margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 10px;margin-left: 16px;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);min-height: 1em;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">因为对用人单位来说，在无法对高校人才培养质量进行量化评价的情况下，依据985、211等标签来筛选求职者显然更简单高效，很多人还会形成一种固化观念：985、211毕业的学生大多都是优秀的，有些名企甚至以此作为招人的门槛。所以相比普通高校毕业的学生来说，名校毕业的学生更容易找到工作，也就是</span><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%;color: rgb(55, 74, 174);box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">“用起来好用”</span></strong><span style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">。</span></span><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span></section><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"></p><section style="margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 10px;margin-left: 16px;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);min-height: 1em;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">最后，名校毕业的学生刚毕业所赚取的薪资是明显高于普通高校的毕业生。</span></section><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"></p><section style="margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 10px;margin-left: 16px;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);min-height: 1em;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">中国薪酬网公布的2018年中国大学毕业生薪酬排行榜TOP200显示，清华大学2017届毕业生以平均月薪9065元位居榜首，但最后一名西安建筑科技大学，2017届毕业生的平均月薪仅有3394元。两所高校毕业生薪资相差了5671元，差距明显，也就是</span><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%;color: rgb(55, 74, 174);box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">“赚得更多”</span></strong><span style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">。</span></span></section><section style="max-width: 100%;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"></p><section style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="padding-right: 3px;padding-bottom: 3px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="padding: 20px 15px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;border-color: rgb(55, 74, 174);border-style: solid;border-width: 1px;box-shadow: rgb(55, 74, 174) 3px 3px 0px 0px;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 10px;margin-left: 16px;max-width: 100%;color: rgb(55, 74, 174);font-size: 14px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img data-type="png" class="" data-ratio="0.5850340136054422" data-w="588" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/UtIAWicWKRfo8ibPEf29tVVeU3fw23BL4HJTiaEsg0jQvcN0Ndp9sTLDF4SkSZaMNNhhXeu6Wc1VyKpH8nibt59jmw/640?wx_fmt=png" style="box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; visibility: visible !important; width: 520px !important; height: auto !important;" _width="520px" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/UtIAWicWKRfo8ibPEf29tVVeU3fw23BL4HJTiaEsg0jQvcN0Ndp9sTLDF4SkSZaMNNhhXeu6Wc1VyKpH8nibt59jmw/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;tp=webp&amp;wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1&amp;wx_co=1" crossorigin="anonymous" data-fail="0"></section></section></section></section><section style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="padding-right: 3px;padding-bottom: 3px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="padding: 20px 15px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;border-color: rgb(55, 74, 174);border-style: solid;border-width: 1px;box-shadow: rgb(55, 74, 174) 3px 3px 0px 0px;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 10px;margin-left: 16px;max-width: 100%;color: rgb(55, 74, 174);font-size: 14px;box-sizing: border-box !im