="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"></p></section><section style="margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 10px;margin-left: 16px;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);min-height: 1em;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">那么全国有多少考生有机会进入“双一流”大学读书呢？</span><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">据透露，<span style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">目前“双一流”(世界一流大学建设高校、世界一流学科建设高校)共计140所，高考招生人数每年大约为37.7万人，占全国招生总量的比例约为4.7%，也就是说录取率预计只有4.7%。</span></span><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span></section><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"></p><section style="margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 10px;margin-left: 16px;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);min-height: 1em;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%;color: rgb(55, 74, 174);font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">3、复读费用也不低</strong><strong style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"></strong></span></section><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"></p><section style="margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 10px;margin-left: 16px;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);min-height: 1em;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">除了学校，有许多考生也选择在各大复读机构进行复读。</span><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">据记者走访发现，广州大部分复读费用在<span style="max-width: 100%;color: rgb(55, 74, 174);box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">4.5万元到6万元</strong></span>不等，其中老牌高复学校卓越的费用最高，一学年收费56780元；</span><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">位居第二的是文德和华兴，其一年学费是53600元。</span><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">所有调查机构中费用较低的是明师复读，它一学年收取的各项费用是40000元。</span></section><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"></p><section style="margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 10px;margin-left: 16px;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);min-height: 1em;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">如果加上日常开销、学习资料等费用，家长还需要花更多的钱让孩子复读。</span><br style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"></section><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"></p><section class="" data-tools="135编辑器" data-id="94065" style="max-width: 100%;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 10px;margin-left: 16px;max-width: 100%;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="max-width: 100%;display: flex;justify-content: center;align-items: center;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="padding: 3px 7px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;display: inline-block;background: rgb(255, 227, 10);border-radius: 6px;font-weight: bold;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">05</span></section><section style="margin-top: 6px;margin-left: 5px;max-width: 100%;display: inline-block;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section class="" data-brushtype="text" style="max-width: 100%;font-weight: bold;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 1.75em;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">什么样的学生适合复读呢？</span></section><section style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;width: 3em;border-bottom: 2px solid rgb(63, 63, 63);float: right;word-wrap: break-word !important;"></section></section></section></section></section><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"></p><section style="margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 10px;margin-left: 16px;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);min-height: 1em;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">有三十几年高三备考经历的语文老师薛蕙表示：</span></section><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"></p><section style="margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 10px;margin-left: 16px;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);min-height: 1em;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">适合复读的是<span style="max-width: 100%;color: rgb(55, 74, 174);box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">“马失前蹄”</strong></span>类型。</span><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">这一类型是指在高考前一年的各大考试中综合成绩（总分）均名列前茅，而本次高考分数未过重本线或超过不多者；</span></section><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"></p><section style="margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 10px;margin-left: 16px;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);min-height: 1em;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">再者是<span style="max-width: 100%;color: rgb(55, 74, 174);box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">“中低平衡”</strong></span>者，在高三一年历次大考中成绩中等，无明显的薄弱学科（跛科）和学科内无明显的知识短板，每次考试均在400分左右徘徊；</span></section><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"></p><section style="margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 10px;margin-left: 16px;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);min-height: 1em;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">另外，“拾级而上”和“笨鸟先飞”两种类型的学生适合复读。</span></section><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"></p><section style="margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 10px;margin-left: 16px;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);min-height: 1em;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%;color: rgb(55, 74, 174);box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">“拾级而上”</strong></span>的考生高二期末考试成绩较差，处于整体水平的下游，但在高三一年历次大考中的成绩每次都有进步，尽管名次上升不多，但一直往上走，本次高考未达理想目标。</span></section><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"></p><section style="margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 10px;margin-left: 16px;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);min-height: 1em;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">而<span style="max-width: 100%;color: rgb(55, 74, 174);box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">“笨鸟先飞”</strong></span>类型考生高考中成绩很差，大部分在360分以下或更少，但他们决心异常坚定，毅力异常强大，尤其是他们有良好的学习习惯，会学习，会思考，会举一反三，融会贯通。</span></section><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"></p><section style="margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 10px;margin-left: 16px;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);min-height: 1em;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">所以，考生选择复读需要非常谨慎。</span></section><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"></p><section style="margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 10px;margin-left: 16px;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);min-height: 1em;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">复读生数量逐年增加，与此同时不少应届高考生在喊“冤”：</span><span style="max-width: 100%;color: rgb(55, 74, 174);font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;">竞争激烈了！</strong><strong style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"></strong></span></section><p style="max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;"></p><section class="" d